Package io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.annotation.data

Annotation Interface Datagen

@Retention(SOURCE) @Target(TYPE) @Documented public @interface Datagen
Registers a class as a data provider to be used in datagen. A class annotated with this must extend DataProvider and define exactly one constructor that must be public. The arguments of the constructor must all be from the list below. Each argument type is optional. Also the order of the arguments does not matter. Allowed argument types for the constructor:
    • ModX
      DataProvider
      ExistingFileHelper
